<h4 class="comment-title"><span  class=" invisible" >no subject</span></h4><span class="poster comment-poster"> <span lj:user="transitional_writes" style="white-space: nowrap;" class="ljuser"><a href="profile"><img src="https://www.dreamwidth.org/img/silk/identity/user.png" alt="[personal profile] " width="17" height="17" style="vertical-align: text-bottom; border: 0; padding-right: 1px;" /></a><a href="index.html"><b>transitional_writes</b></a></span></span>
<span class="datetime"><span class="comment-date-text"> </span> <span title="15 minutes after journal entry">2026-03-14 07:50 am (UTC)</span></span><span class="commentpermalink">(<a href="40305.html?thread=21873#cmt21873">link</a>)</span>
